 segments electricity segment and product segment the company also manufactures products that produce electricity from recovered energy or socalled waste heat it also constructs owns and operates recovered energybased power plantselectricity segmentthe companys electricity segment develops builds owns and operates geothermal and recovered energybased power plants in the united states and geothermal power plants in other countries around the world and sells the electricity it generates the companys geothermal power plants are located in california which include ormesa complex heber complex mammoth complex and north brawley west nevada which include steamboat complex and brady complex east nevada including tuscarora jersey valley mcginness hills and don a campbell hawaii which include puna and international which include amatitlan zunil and olkaria iii complex the company also owns and operates recovered energy generation reg power plants which include oreg  oreg  oreg  and oreg product segmentthe companys product segment designs manufactures and sells equipment for geothermal and recovered energybased electricity generation and remote power units and provide services relating to the engineering procurement construction operation and maintenance of geothermal and recovered energybased power plants it designs manufactures and sells power units for geothermal electricity generation which is referred to as ormat energy converter oecs the company offers oecs to contractors and geothermal power plant developers owners and operators the company also offers power units used to generate electricity from recovered energy it offers power units for recovered energybased power generation to interstate natural gas pipeline owners and operators gas processing plant owners and operators cement plant owners and operators and other companies engaged in other energyintensive industrial processes the company engineers procures and constructs as engineering procurement and construction epc contractor geothermal and recovered energy power plants on a turnkey basis the company designs manufactures and sells fossil fuel powered turbogenerators with capacities ranging from  watts to  watts the company offers turbogenerators to contractors installing gas pipelines in remote areas and offshore platforms operators and contractors in addition the company designs manufactures and sells generators including heavy duty directcurrent generators for various other usesthe company competes with calenergy calpine corporation terragen power llc enel green power spa mercury contact energy energy development corporation mitsubishi hitachi power systems fuji electric co ltd toshiba genuovo pignone brand ansaldo energia atlas copco company exergy ge geothermal energy research  development co ltd and global thermoelectric » full overview of ora company address ormat technologies inc  neil rd ste reno   nv    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation isaac angel  doron blachar  bob sullivan  shlomi argas  shimon hatzir  » more officers  directors ormat technologies inc news brieformat secures first portfolio power purchase agreement for  mw of geothermal capacity jun   briefmigdal insurance  financial holdings reports  pct passive stake in ormat technologies may   japans orix to buy  percent of israel geothermal energy firm ormat may   japans orix to buy  pct of israel geothermal energy firm ormat may   brieformat technologies says orix corp to acquire  stake in ormat for about  mln may   » more ora news related topics stocksstock screenerutilitieselectric utilities ora profile  ormat technologies inc stock  yahoo financehomemailflickrtumblrnewssportsfinancecelebrityanswersgroupsmobilemoreyahoosearchsearchus markets closedsp  dow  ormat technologies inc oranyse  nyse delayed price currency in usdadd to watchlist at close pm edtpeople also watchhtmitricvaamscidasummaryconversationsstatisticsprofilefinancialsoptionsholdershistorical dataanalyst