rtisement events add ora to my calendars aug   q  ormat technologies inc earnings call  am edt  aug   q  ormat technologies inc earnings release  am edt  jun   ormat technologies inc at roth cleantech  industrial growth day may   q  ormat technologies inc earnings call  may   q  ormat technologies inc earnings release may   ormat technologies inc annual shareholders meeting more events from dailyfinance »     key stats and ratios q mar   net profit margin   operating margin   ebitd margin   return on average assets   return on average equity   employees   cdp score  d screen stocks with similar metrics » address  neil rd ste reno nv united states  map phone fax website links httpwwwormatcom external links analyst estimates  marketwatch sec filings  edgar online major holders  msn money research reports  reuters settings  technicals  link to this view volume delayed by  minsprices are not from all markets sources include six advertisement related companies show most recent quarter most recent annual add or remove columns save changes cancel sector utilities  industry electric utilities  nec more from factset » description ormat technologies inc is engaged in the geothermal and recovered energy power business the company designs develops builds owns and operates geothermal and recovered energybased power plants its equipment manufacturing operations are located in israel it conducts its business activities in two business segments electricity segment and product segment the electricity segment develops builds owns and operates geothermal and recovered energybased power plants in the united states and geothermal power plants in other countries around the world and sells the electricity it generates the product segment designs manufactures and sells equipment for geothermal and recovered energybased electricity generation and remote power units and provide services relating to the engineering procurement construction operation and maintenance of geothermal and recovered energybased power plants it manufactures products that produce electricity from recovered energy or waste heat more from reuters » officers and directors isaac angel chief executive officer age  bio  compensation   reuters doron blachar chief financial officer age  bio  compensation   reuters bob sullivan executive vice president  sales and marketing and business development age  bio  compensation   reuters shlomi argas executive vice president  projects age  bio  compensation   reuters shimon hatzir executive vice president  engineering age  bio  compensation   reuters erez klein executive vice president  production age  bio  compensation   reuters zvi krieger executive vice president  electricity segment age  bio  compensation   reuters nir wolf executive vice president  market development age  bio  compensation   reuters etty rosner senior vice president  contract management corporate secretary age  bio  compensation   reuters ravit barniv independent director age  bio  compensation   reuters full list on reuters » google finance beta available in hong kong  canada  us  china  ukinformation is provided as is and solely for informational purposes not for trading purposes or advice and may be delayedto see all exchange delays please see disclaimer google  google home  blog  help  report a problem  privacy policy  terms of service ormat technologies inc  geothermal energy  organic rankine cycle search this site english español home solutions technology company news research center investor relations global projects contact us careers our company ormat technologies inc nyse oraa leading vertically integrated global provider of a diverse range of renewable energy solutionsread more   our history technology news july   ormat technologies inc to host conference call announcing second quarter  financial results read more june   ormat secures first portfolio ppa for  mw of geothermal capacity with scppa read more all press releasesbrochures spotlight join the ormat q fin